Author: sixteen_sosweet
Text: thank you. id heard before that its normal, but reassurance helps. it just... feels like im binging and have no control, but I'm trying to understand that i actually need to be eating above maintenance to become a healthy weight again

Author: stevemurkle
Text: it's SUPER normal to have extreme hunger during refeeding or w/e you want to call it. i get that it /feels/ like binging, but your body probably just really wants/needs to be fed
